'''[[Orion]] [[nebula|Nebula]]'''

#{{astronomy}}: A [[diffuse]] [[nebula]] visible in the night sky below [[Orion's Belt]]; it is approximately 40 [[light year]]s across. It is one of the brightest nebulae visible to the naked eye and is the closest region of [[stellar]] formation to Earth.